=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
שׁקה / shâqâh / shaw-kaw' 

=== Etymology ===

A primitive root; 
=== Verb ===
to quaff, that is, (causatively) to irrigate or furnish a potion to: - cause to (give, give to, let, make to) drink, drown, moisten, water. See {{HH|7937}}, {{HH|8354}}.